title: Google\Cloud\Talent\V4beta1\BatchDeleteJobsRequest
name: BatchDeleteJobsRequest
description:
Batch delete jobs request.

Generated from protobuf message google.cloud.talent.v4beta1.BatchDeleteJobsRequest

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.parent
params.description: Required. The resource name of the tenant under which the job is created. The format is "projects/{project_id}/tenants/{tenant_id}". For example, "projects/foo/tenant/bar". If tenant id is unspecified, a default tenant is created. For example, "projects/foo".

params.name: data.filter
params.description: Required. The filter string specifies the jobs to be deleted. Supported operator: =, AND The fields eligible for filtering are: companyName (Required) requisitionId (Required) Sample Query: companyName = "projects/foo/companies/bar" AND requisitionId = "req-1"
